OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FAssessment forms completed for triple
OL,8,Fkiller Valdo Calocane before he killed
OL,9,Fthree people, failed to detail the
OL,10,Flevel of risk he posed, the inquiry
OL,11,Finto the Nottingham attacks heard.
OL,13,FCalocane killed two 19-year-old
OL,14,Fstudents, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and
OL,15,FBarnaby Webber, and grandfather Ian
OL,16,FCoates on June 13 2023 in Nottingham
OL,17,Fbefore seriously harming others.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
