FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FCalocane had been under the care of
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust for two years prior
OL,10,Fto the stabbing, during which time he
OL,11,Fwas repeatedly discharged despite a
OL,12,Fconsultant psychiatrist warning that
OL,13,Fhe would "end up killing someone".
OL,15,FCalocane was previously diagnosed with
OL,16,Fparanoid schizophrenia in 2020 and he
OL,17,Fwas sentenced to a hospital order in
OL,18,FJanuary 2024 after the attacks.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FHis actions are now being examined as
OL,8,Fpart of the Nottingham Inquiry, which
OL,9,Fis hearing from more than 100
OL,10,Fwitnesses and has been running since
OL,11,FFebruary.
OL,13,FHealthcare professionals from the
OL,14,Ftrust gave evidence to the inquiry as
OL,15,Fpart of an examination into the
OL,16,Ftrust's mental health services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FCalocane was first detained in May
OL,8,F2020 after he repeatedly kicked at the
OL,9,Fdoor of a property, leading the 22-
OL,10,Fyear-old woman inside to severely
OL,11,Fdamage her spine while trying to
OL,12,Fescape through a window.
OL,14,FHe was discharged a month later
OL,15,Fdespite having told doctors he "wanted
OL,16,Fto hurt... permanently", according to
OL,17,Fmedical records.
OL,26,@wD@`OUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FHe was then sectioned again in July
OL,8,F2020 after forcibly entering a
OL,9,Fneighbour's flat and later in
OL,10,FSeptember 2021 after he "significantly
OL,11,Fassaulted" police officers who
OL,12,Fattended in support for a Mental
OL,13,FHealth Act assessment.
OL,15,FBusayo Ajewole, the clinical team
OL,16,Fleader at Highbury Hospital,
OL,17,FNottingham, where Calocane was
OL,18,Fsectioned in July 2020, admitted to
OL,19,Ffilling out multiple risk assessment
OL,20,Fforms incorrectly for Calocane during
OL,21,Fthe inquiry on Monday.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FJulian Blake KC, counsel for the
OL,8,FNottingham Inquiry, highlighted to the
OL,9,Finquiry that the forms failed to
OL,10,Fclearly detail Calocane's level of
OL,11,Fviolence and risk.
OL,13,FMr Blake showed the inquiry the risk
OL,14,Fassessment form completed in July
OL,15,F2020, where Calocane was said to have
OL,16,Fhad "no history of mental health
OL,17,Fdifficulties" and "no history of
OL,18,Fviolence and aggression".
OL,26,@xD@EOUyD@MO]yD@SOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FMs Ajewol agreed this was "not only
OL,8,Flacking in detail but that's also
OL,9,Fwrong".
OL,11,FShe told the inquiry: "Yes. I
OL,12,Funderstand it should have reflected
OL,13,Fthat he had a history of violence and
OL,14,Faggression in the risk assessment."
OL,16,FThe inquiry also heard there was a
OL,17,Flack of evidence in entries from
OL,18,FSeptember 2021 on Calocane's risk
OL,19,Fassessment forms.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@FO]sD@WOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FMr Blake highlighted that his level of
OL,8,Fviolence and risk was not clearly
OL,9,Fidentified, and the form was again
OL,10,F"wrong".
OL,12,FOne of the documents shown to the
OL,13,Finquiry used the phrase "Valdo is
OL,14,Fusually a very polite and gentle
OL,15,Fpersonable young man", of which Ms
OL,16,FAjewol could not identify where that
OL,17,Fwording had come from.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@GO]uD@YOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777370785
OL,3,CInquiry: Valdo Calocane risk
OL,4,Cassessment forms were 'fundamentally
OL,5,Cwrong'
OL,7,FErrors on the risk assessment form
OL,8,Fwere again replicated in a summary and
OL,9,Fcare plan for Calocane shown to the
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,FMs Ajewol was asked to reflect on her
OL,13,Fduty to submit accurate records by Mr
OL,14,FBlake, after agreeing her notes were
OL,15,F"quite fundamentally wrong".
OL,17,FShe also admitted she had failed to
OL,18,Frecord two violence and aggression
OL,19,Fmarkers on Nottinghamshire Healthcare
OL,20,Ftrust's system.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
